PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of DORAMY EHLING of Richmond, British Columbia, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Marianne D.
